fect example of how educational games can make learning complex concepts enjoyable and interactive. So next time you’re looking for a brain workout or a way to improve your problem-solving skills, give the Hooda Math Traveling Salesman puzzle a try—you might be surprised at how much you learn while trying to find that shortest path.",
